The Press: I'm curious whether
the President has reached out

00:10:32.965 --> 00:10:34.000
to Kanye West

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.968
and whether he'd be willing
to meet with him

00:10:35.968 --> 00:10:37.303
at the White House.

00:10:37.303 --> 00:10:39.038
Ms. Sanders: I don't know
of any conversation

00:10:39.038 --> 00:10:42.742
that they've had over
the last week or so.

00:10:43.609 --> 00:10:45.678
I'll keep you posted
if that changes at any time.

00:10:45.678 --> 00:10:46.579
Matthew.

00:10:46.579 --> 00:10:48.080
The Press: Two weeks ago?

00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:50.282
Ms. Sanders:  Sorry, I know
they met during the transition.

00:10:50.282 --> 00:10:51.550
That's the only meeting
I'm aware

00:10:51.550 --> 00:10:53.319
of that's taken place
for a conversation.

00:10:54.787 --> 00:10:57.023
Before everybody has
a meltdown and thinks

00:10:57.023 --> 00:10:58.958
that we had a meeting last week.

